Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.74,0:16:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想更臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,栗山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你闻闻  这么臭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,莫名其妙  一直都这么臭下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想再臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那我又该怎么办啊
